data.description: **OPEN HOUSE Sat 1/6 12-3pm **Welcome to this beautiful home conveniently located 10min from Randolph AFB and 30 min from Ft Sam Houston. As you enter the home you will find a formal dining room. Following the entry hallway will take you into a stunning open kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, tile backsplash, walk in pantry, lots of cabinet space and a large eat-in breakfast bar. Refrigerator is included. The kitchen opens to a spacious living room, complete with a stunning vaulted ceiling. A half bathroom is located off the family room . The private main bedroom suite is located on the first floor off the family room.It offers dual vanities, separate tub and shower, ceramic tile flooring, large walk-in closet. oversized utility room is located off the kitchen by the stairs. The second floor includes a spacious game room, a second full bath, and three large secondary bedrooms with walk-in closets. Ceramic tile flooring throughout the first in entryway, family room, kitchen, dining room, bathrooms and utility room.   Full Interior paint just done. Private backyard with no neighbors directly behind it. Schertz-Cibolo-Universal City ISDS. Schedule your showing today!!
